<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694236>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Male genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A, B—Lomographa bimaculata; C, D—L. temerata; E, F—Earoxyptera buraetica; G—I—Odontopera bidentata; J, K—Crocallis elinguaria. A, C, E, G, K—genital segment; B, C, F, H–J—phallos. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694236/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694280>
    dc:description "FIGURE 31. Female genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A—Cabera exanthemata; B–C. pusaria; C—C. leptographa; D— Eilicrinia unimacularia; E—Astegania honesta; F—Lomographa bimaculata; G—L. temerata; H—Earoxyptera buraetica. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4694280/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

